mit 2019.”&nbsp;Last modified September 24, 2019.&nbsp;Accessed May 21, 2020.&nbsp;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://pib.gov.in/PressReleaseIframePage.aspx?PRID=1586051" target="_blank">https://pib.gov.in/PressReleaseIframePage.aspx?PRID=1586051</a>.&nbsp;</div></li><li><span>16</span><div>Tooze, Adam.&nbsp;“Why Central Banks Need to Step UP on Global Warming.”&nbsp;<em>Foreign Policy</em>, last modified&nbsp;July 20, 2019.&nbsp;Accessed May 21, 2020.&nbsp;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/07/20/why-central-banks-need-to-step-up-on-global-warming/" target="_blank">https://foreignpolicy.com/2019/07/20/why-central-banks-need-to-step-up-on-global-warming/</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></li><li><span>17</span><div>Carney, Mark.&nbsp;<em>Breaking the tragedy of the horizon – climate change and financial stability</em>. Speech by&nbsp;the&nbsp;Governor of the Bank of England and Chairman of the Financial Stability Board at Lloyd’s of London.&nbsp;&nbsp;Accessed May 21, 2020.&nbsp;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.bis.org/review/r151009a.pdf" target="_blank">https://www.bis.org/review/r151009a.pdf</a>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></li><li><span>18</span><div>Jones, Huw. “Global regulators hold off designating&nbsp;‘too big to fail’&nbsp;insurers.”&nbsp;<em>Reuters</em>, last&nbsp;modified November 14, 2018.&nbsp;Accessed May 21, 2020.&nbsp;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://in.reuters.com/article/g20-insurance-regulator/global-regulators-hold-off-designating-too-big-to-fail-insurers-idINKCN1NJ2K3" target="_blank">https://in.reuters.com/article/g20-insurance-regulator/global-regulators-hold-off-designating-too-big-to-fail-insurers-idINKCN1NJ2K3</a>.</div></li><li><span>19</span><div>William, Jessica, Micheal T.Ferguson, Miroslav Petkov, and Michael Wilkins.&nbsp;<em>The Effects of Weather Events on Corporate Earnings Are Gathering Force.</em>&nbsp;London: S&amp;P Ratings (June 2018).</div></li><li><span>20</span><div>Ocampo, José A